Package: criteval
Title: Simulations and Comparisons of Splitting Criteria for Generalized
    Random Forests
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("David", "Fleischer", , "david.p.fleischer@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut"))
Description: An evaluation framework for the simulation and comparison of
    splitting criteria used by GRF in its recursive partitioning
    mechanism, particularly for causal forests and multi-dimensional
    varying-coefficient models.
